    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can make a melee&nbsp;<em>touch attack</em>&nbsp;as a&nbsp;<em>standard action</em>&nbsp;that inflicts 1d4 points of&nbsp;<em>nonlethal damage</em>&nbsp;+ 1 for every two sorcerer levels you possess. In addition, the target is&nbsp;<em>dazzled</em>&nbsp;for 1 minute. Creatures with&nbsp;<em>low-light vision</em>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<em>darkvision</em>&nbsp;are not&nbsp;<em>dazzled</em>&nbsp;by this ability. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<em>Charisma</em>&nbsp;modifier.</p>"
